{\sum_{j'=1}^{N_k} \exp(S_{ij'}) + \exp(S_h)}Pij​=∑j′=1Nk​​exp(Sij′​)+exp(Sh​)exp(Sij​)​ Where: Sink Probability: The sink probability is computed but not used in the output: Pi,h=exp⁡(Sh)∑j′=1Nkexp⁡(Sij′)+exp⁡(Sh)P_{i,h}
=
