{\sum_{j'=1}^{N_k} \exp(S_{ij'}) + \exp(S_h)}Pi,h​=∑j′=1Nk​​exp(Sij′​)+exp(Sh​)exp(Sh​)​ The gradient of the loss L with respect to the sink parameter Shis: ∂L∂Sh=−∑iPi,h(∂L∂Si,h−∑j∈{1,…,Nk}Pij∂L∂Sij)\frac{\partial L}{\partial S_h}
=
